Time Duration: 45 ~ 60  minutes
Topics to be covered:
1. What is Automation and RPA?
2. RPA vs normal automation (probably using Selenium a quick go through) ~> basically why I insist  over RPA when we talk about automation
   The important difference that I want to show is the term "low code / No code"
3.  Few Bot Examples:
     1~> Table data scrapping (can be made during presentation 3-4 minutes): Structured Data
     2 ~> Pattern Based Data Scrapping (can be made during presentation  3-4 minutes ): Semi-Structured Data
     3 ~> LinkedIn Profile Scrapper(Live Running Demo) : Unstructured Data
4. Installation Guide and how to start journey with RPA
